{"word":"H2250 - חַבּוּרָה - chabbûwrâh - khab-boo-raw' - Blueness","slug":"H2250","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">חַבּוּרָה</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>chabbûwrâh"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>khab-boo-raw'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Blueness"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x05D7;&#x05D1;&#x05E8;&#x05D4;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&#x05D7;&#x05D1;&#x05BC;&#x05E8;&#x05D4;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&#x05D7;&#x05D1;&#x05BC;&#x05D5;&#x05BC;&#x05E8;&#x05D4; - chabbu&#x0302;ra&#x0302;h  chabbu&#x0302;ra&#x0302;h  cha&#x0306;bu&#x0302;ra&#x0302;h</b> - <i>(1,2) khab-boo-raw', (3) khab-oo-raw'</i><p/>From <a href=\"#/H2266\">H2266</a>; properly <i>bound</i> (with stripes), that is, a <i>weal</i> (or black and blue mark itself): - blueness, bruise, hurt, stripe, wound."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H2249\">H2249</a>, <a href=\"#/H2266\">H2266</a>, <a href=\"#/H2267\">H2267</a>, <a href=\"#/H2268\">H2268</a>, <a href=\"#/H2270\">H2270</a>, <a href=\"#/H2271\">H2271</a>, <a href=\"#/H2272\">H2272</a>, <a href=\"#/H2274\">H2274</a>, <a href=\"#/H2275\">H2275</a>, <a href=\"#/H2276\">H2276</a>, <a href=\"#/H2277\">H2277</a>, <a href=\"#/H2278\">H2278</a>, <a href=\"#/H2279\">H2279</a>, <a href=\"#/H4225\">H4225</a>, <a href=\"#/H4226\">H4226</a>"}]}